                <p class="card_mode">FRONT END</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card" id="upload-de-imagens-no-s3-da-aws-com-node-js/">
            <div class="card_image">
                <img src="https://blog.rocketseat.com.br/content/images/2020/09/upload-de-imagens-no-s3-da-aws-com-node-js.png" alt="">
            </div>
            <div class="card_content">
                <p>Upload de imagens no S3 da AWS com NodeJS</p>
                <p>por <a href="https://blog.rocketseat.com.br/author/thiago/" target="_blank" rel="">Thiago Marinho</a></p>
