        </div>
        <div class="card" id="axios-um-cliente-http-full-stack/">
            <div class="card_image">
                <img src="https://blog.rocketseat.com.br/content/images/2020/09/axios-um-cliente-http-full-stack-rocketseat.png" alt="">
            </div>
            <div class="card_content">
                <p>Axios - um cliente HTTP Full Stack</p>
                <p>por <a href="https://blog.rocketseat.com.br/author/thiago/" target="_blank" rel="">Thiago Marinho</a></p>
            </div>
            <div class="card_info">
                <p><img class="imgpng" src="time.png" alt=""> 10 min de Leitura</p>
                <p class="card_mode">FRONT END</p>
            </div>
        </div>
